Solaria Agrees to Buy Back Up to 10% of Spanish Solar Company’s Shares

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-05-19T10:08:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/solaria-agrees-to-buy-back-up-to-10-of-spanish-solar-company-s-shares.html
Solaria Energia y Medio Ambiente SA (SLR) 
approved a plan to buy back as much as 10 percent of the
company’s shares, the company said in a regulatory filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
